d failures.\n\n### Results JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend-0->AdService/GetAds\",\n    \"frontend-1->AdService/GetAds\",\n    \"status_code_2\",\n    \"timeout_error\",\n    \"slow_response\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"AdService exhibits significant latency spike (~2x increase) and error rates (status code 2). These anomalies coincide with downstream frontend failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Trace data for operations 'frontend-0->AdService/GetAds' and 'frontend-1->AdService/GetAds' showing latency spike and error occurrences.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
